# Quell UI

- Match existing popup/options structure: plain HTML + CSS + small TS controller (no React).
- Talk to the SW only through `Message` types; never poke DNR APIs from the UI.
- Keep the UI dense and clear (product UI, not marketing). Reuse existing class names and spacing.
- After UI TS/HTML/CSS changes, `npm run bundle` (or `watch`) and reload the extension to verify.
